ActAeronautics Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (PART V) by introducing procedures that will require applicants seeking approval of design changes to aeronautical products (e.g., aircraft frames, engines or propellers) to incorporate the most current design standards into the redesigned products to the greatest extent practicable.
